Yes.

54:03.410 --> 54:05.173
I was at the university, and I'm 20, by the way.

54:05.373 --> 54:06.414
Okay, 20 years old.

54:06.915 --> 54:08.117
And so you were at...

54:08.570 --> 54:12.636
You told me last night, I wanted to tell you again, where you were going to school.

54:13.677 --> 54:14.919
Idaho State University.

54:15.059 --> 54:15.920
And you were studying?

54:15.980 --> 54:22.889
