54:29.078 --> 54:33.464
I'm technically an English major, but... Are you a freshman?

54:33.784 --> 54:34.665
Technically I am.

54:34.725 --> 54:38.070
It's kind of weird, because I've got three semesters, so...

54:38.894 --> 54:40.076
Your sophomore?

54:40.096 --> 54:40.637
I guess so.

54:41.338 --> 54:50.071
And English major, I'm kind of an English major, but I guess writing, is this something that was going to you?

54:50.091 --> 54:50.712
Absolutely.

