Writing's always been the biggest thing to have told me.

54:54.478 --> 55:00.006
But you don't need a degree in writing to be a writer.

55:01.348 --> 55:02.931
Okay.

55:03.812 --> 55:05.695
And I've always loved journalism school.

55:06.535 --> 55:11.943
Nobody learns how to be a journalist, but no IJ is a cool person to learn about doing it.

55:11.963 --> 55:19.935
And so, uh, you can tell me about how hard you can hear it, what can your calculus work that brings to this place sometimes.

